																		New Hell Tale Posted
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thefriendlyvandal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2064544); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2064544&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610163013" alt="thefriendlyvandal" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2064544)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thefriendlyvandal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2064544); return false;" >thefriendlyvandal</a></span> <span class="odate time_1506837671 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">01 Oct 2017 06:01</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3605216">
									

<p>Wow, this sure is a wild time.</p>
<p>Some things and stuff:</p>
<p>1. Draven actually&#8230;isn't my character? This is the first time he's been put on-site, but he actually belongs to <a href="http://v1als.tumblr.com/">V1als on tumblr.</a> James is mine. They're dorks. (EDIT as of November 15th, 2017): James is actually James Talloran from SCP-3999. It's canon now, as in, it's in the actual 3999 article. We made it big lads</p>
<p>2. Parts of this tale are meta. What can you do.</p>
<p>3. This is so long, like yikes.</p>
<p>4. Just like <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/your-circuits-dead-theres-something-wrong">Major Tom</a>, I never meant for this to get this long and go on the site. This started as a fanfic. Unlike Major Tom, this took me probably a week of binge writing to finish as opposed to eight months.</p>
<p>5. This doesn't take place in the Major Tom universe. That's not to say that I'm not working on a ton of new stuff to go in the Major Tom universe, though.</p>
<p>6. I'm&#8230;not sure how happy I am with this, but it's&#8230;okay.</p>
<p>7. Stephen King's <em>Pet Sematary</em> is amazing and you should read it.</p>

							</div>

								
